  "title": "Create: Farming & Delights!",
  "description": "Combining the Create Mod with Farmer's Delight plus a little QoL and worldgen",
  "body": "![Create: Farming and Delights](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6358dbc8088d3db70785bb1a232c3e77ea2ed922.png)\n\n<a href=\"https://github.com/BurningButter/create-farmersdelight\"><img alt=\"github\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/available/github_vector.svg\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/modpack/cAh2fjKY/versions\"><img alt=\"fabric\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/supported/fabric_vector.svg\"></a>\n\nA modpack with the goal of bridging the gap between Create and Farmer's Delight, while including a few nifty addons for both mods and maintaining decent performance.\n\n## Important Note\nThis was my first ever published modpack and is not a very cohesive experience. It is mostly me dumping a bunch of mods and only doing tweaks to get the packs to work together. If you are looking for a complete and well integrated experience you might enjoy something like [Raspberry Flavored](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/raspberry-flavoured), my all time favorite modpack which does include both Create and Farmer's Delight with fantastic integration.\n\n## Included mods\n<details>\n<summary>Farmer's Delight</summary>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/R2OftAxM\" target=\"_blank\">Farmer's Delight</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/e9V6wFcR\" target=\"_blank\">Expanded Delight</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/bCxmmxKN\" target=\"_blank\">Overweight Farming</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/9rlXSyLg\" target=\"_blank\">Crate Delight</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/MIdaKqt7\" target=\"_blank\">Fishing Real</a></li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Create</summary>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ysHf2zCJ\" target=\"_blank\">Create (Fabric Sodium Fix)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/GmjmRQ0A\" target=\"_blank\">Create Slice & Dice</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/sMvUb4Rb\" target=\"_blank\">Create Deco</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/UT2M39wf\" target=\"_blank\">Create: Copycats+</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/L1RT5SJc\" target=\"_blank\">Create Goggles</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ZzjhlDgM\" target=\"_blank\">Create: Steam 'n' Rails</a></li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Worldgen</summary>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/8oi3bsk5\" target=\"_blank\">Terralith</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fgmhI8kH\" target=\"_blank\">ChoiceTheorem's Overhauled Village</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/t5FRdP87\" target=\"_blank\">YUNG's Better Witch Huts</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/HjmxVlSr\" target=\"_blank\">YUNG's Better Mineshafts</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/kidLKymU\" target=\"_blank\">YUNG's Better Strongholds</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/Z2mXHnxP\" target=\"_blank\">YUNG's Better Nether Fortresses</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/XNlO7sBv\" target=\"_blank\">YUNG's Better Desert Temples</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/o1C1Dkj5\" target=\"_blank\">YUNG's Better Dungeons</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/3dT9sgt4\" target=\"_blank\">YUNG's Better Ocean Monuments</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/2BwBOmBQ\" target=\"_blank\">YUNG's Better End Island</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/z9Ve58Ih\" target=\"_blank\">YUNG's Better Jungle Temples</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ZYgyPyfq\" target=\"_blank\">YUNG's Extras</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/Ht4BfYp6\" target=\"_blank\">YUNG's Bridges</a></li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Experience</summary>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/YL57xq9U\" target=\"_blank\">Iris</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/1IjD5062\" target=\"_blank\">Continuity</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/yBW8D80W\" target=\"_blank\">LambDynamicLights</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/rcTfTZr3\" target=\"_blank\">Presence Footsteps</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/qyVF9oeo\" target=\"_blank\">Sound Physics Remastered</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fM515JnW\" target=\"_blank\">AmbientSounds</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/rI0hvYcd\" target=\"_blank\">Visuality</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/WhbRG4iK\" target=\"_blank\">Falling Leaves</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/89Wsn8GD\" target=\"_blank\">Capes</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/resourcepack/dspVZXKP\" target=\"_blank\">Fast Better Grass</a> (Texture Pack)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/resourcepack/Srw5RQ6k\" target=\"_blank\">xali's Enhanced Vanilla</a> (Texture Pack)</li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Optimization</summary>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/AANobbMI\" target=\"_blank\">Sodium</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/PtjYWJkn\" target=\"_blank\">Sodium Extra</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/gvQqBUqZ\" target=\"_blank\">Lithium</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/5ZwdcRci\" target=\"_blank\">ImmediatelyFast</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/LQ3K71Q1\" target=\"_blank\">Dynamic FPS</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/uXXizFIs\" target=\"_blank\">FerriteCore</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/NRjRiSSD\" target=\"_blank\">Memory Leak Fix</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/VSNURh3q\" target=\"_blank\">Concurrent Chunk Management Engine</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/NNAgCjsB\" target=\"_blank\">Entity Culling</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/H8CaAYZC\" target=\"_blank\">Starlight</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/51shyZVL\" target=\"_blank\">More Culling</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/nmDcB62a\" target=\"_blank\">ModernFix</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/OVuFYfre\" target=\"_blank\">Enhanced Block Entities</a></li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Useful bits</summary>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/mOgUt4GM\" target=\"_blank\">Mod Menu</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/u6dRKJwZ\" target=\"_blank\">Just Enough Items</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/Bh37bMuy\" target=\"_blank\">Reese's Sodium Options</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/kzwxhsjp\" target=\"_blank\">Accurate Block Placement Reborn</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/litematica\" target=\"_blank\">Litematica</a> (This mod is from Curseforge!)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/9eGKb6K1\" target=\"_blank\">Simple Voice Chat</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/w7ThoJFB\" target=\"_blank\">Zoomify</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/qQyHxfxd\" target=\"_blank\">No Chat Reports</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/REfW2AEX\" target=\"_blank\">InvMove</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/DOUdJVEm\" target=\"_blank\">Controlify</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/x1hIzbuY\" target=\"_blank\">FastQuit</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/EsAfCjCV\" target=\"_blank\">AppleSkin</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/UVtY3ZAC\" target=\"_blank\">Enchantment Descriptions</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/8shC1gFX\" target=\"_blank\">BetterF3</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/kYq5qkSL\" target=\"_blank\">Borderless Mining</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/kqJFAPU9\" target=\"_blank\">Better Mount HUD</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/G1epq3jN\" target=\"_blank\">AdvancementInfo</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/u5Ic2U1u\" target=\"_blank\">Mouse Wheelie</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/WwbubTsV\" target=\"_blank\">YOSBR</a></li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Libraries, APIs, and other stuff</summary>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/P7dR8mSH\" target=\"_blank\">Fabric API</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/9s6osm5g\" target=\"_blank\">Cloth Config API</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/lhGA9TYQ\" target=\"_blank\">Architectury API</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/Ha28R6CL\" target=\"_blank\">Fabric Language Kotlin</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/Orvt0mRa\" target=\"_blank\">Indium</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/XaDC71GB\" target=\"_blank\">Lithostitched</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/OsZiaDHq\" target=\"_blank\">CreativeCore</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/Ua7DFN59\" target=\"_blank\">YUNG's API</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/GcWjdA9I\" target=\"_blank\">MaLiLib</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/QdG47OkI\" target=\"_blank\">Model Gap Fix</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/QwxR6Gcd\" target=\"_blank\">Debugify</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ZP7xHXtw\" target=\"_blank\">Remove Reloading Screen</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/CdRC4fyI\" target=\"_blank\">CTOV - Farmer Delight Compat</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/HdwRs3kc\" target=\"_blank\">Disable Custom Worlds Advice</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/sk4iFZGy\" target=\"_blank\">Remove Terralith Intro Message</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/1eAoo2KR\" target=\"_blank\">YetAnotherConfigLib</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/uy4Cnpcm\" target=\"_blank\">Bookshelf</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fuuu3xnx\" target=\"_blank\">Searchables</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ohNO6lps\" target=\"_blank\">Forge Config API Port</a></li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n\nPlease [inform me](https://github.com/BurningButter/create-farmersdelight/issues/new) if any links or formatting are broken, I'm missing some mods in this list, or if I missed anything else! :)\nFeel free to make suggestions for the pack on github too!",
